WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.420
I have a cold and am taking a day off school.

00:02.980 --> 00:04.820
I’ve stayed home for 3 days now.

00:05.830 --> 00:09.710
The kids at school probably think I’m just cutting school.

00:10.610 --> 00:12.320
None of them visit me.

00:13.240 --> 00:15.560
They don’t like me.
